        "text": "Wiking occupies an unusual position in the Waffen-SS order of battle: although classified administratively as a German Waffen-SS Panzer division, alongside the Leibstandarte, Das Reich, and Totenkopf, its rank and file were drawn overwhelmingly from volunteers outside Germany itself — Norwegians, Danes, Dutch, Finns, and Flemish Belgians — recruited under Himmler's vision of a pan-Germanic, rather than purely German, SS."
